  "id": 9051528757499,
  "title": "950HP Twin Turbos TD04 19T compatible with BMW N54 335i 335xi 335is E90 E91 E92 E93 3.0L FT100310+FT100320",
  "handle": "ft100310-ft100320-900hp-twin-turbos-td04-19t-compatible-with-bmw-n54-335i-335xi-335is-e90-e91-e92-e93-3-0l",
  "description": "<div>\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<li>BMW 335i / 335xi (E90/E91/E92/E93) N54B30 3.0L Turbocharged, 2007-2010</li>\n<li>BMW 335is (E92/E93) N54B30 3.0L Turbocharged, 2011-2013</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"color: #800000; font-weight: bold;\">Will NOT fit 135i, 535i, Z4, X6, 740i</p>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<li>19T design, upgraded forged billet compressor wheel comparable in flow to 19T turbo.</li>\n<li>Enhances vehicle performance and boosts engine power, supports up to 950HP.</li>\n<li>Component balanced, VSR high-speed balanced to avg. 0.5 mg or less.</li>\n<li>Billet stainless steel wastegate flapper valves with thicker rod.</li>\n<li>Requires modification for installation (compressor housing inlet larger than stock). Needs 2\" (55mm) intake hose.</li>\n<li>Includes all accessories shown in photos.</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n<li>Upgraded Forged Billet Compressor Wheel: 12 (6+6) blades, Size: 45.1 × 58 mm</li>\n<li>Turbine Wheel: 9 blades, Size: 41.2 × 47.2 mm</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Turbo Part Numbers:</h4>\n<p>49131-07000, 49131-07001, 49131-07006, 49131-07007, 49131-07010,<br>49131-07011, 49131-07015, 49131-07016, 49131-07107, 49131-07018,<br>49131-07019, 49131-07030, 49131-07031, 49131-07040, 49131-07041,<br>49131-07065, 49131-07066, 49131-07067, 49131-07068, 49131-07069,<br>49131-07075, 49131-07076, 49131-07077, 49131-07078, 49131-07079,<br>49131-07161, 49131-07170, 49131-07180, 49131-07205, 49131-07206</p>\n<h4>OEM Numbers:</h4>\n<p>11654564711, 11654564710, 11657563685, 11657563686, 11657583863,<br>11657583864, 11657593015, 11657593016, 11657649289, 11657649290,<br>4564710, 4564711, 7583863, 7583864, 7593015, 7593016,<br>7563685, 7563686, 7649289, 7649290</p>\n</div>",
